0.1.name: wordpress/uk-lottery-results-widget
0.1.description: Show the latest UK lottery results from Lotto, Thunderball, Euromillions, Lotto Plus 5 and Health Lottery draws on your Wordpress site. As well as just the latest results, further information can be displayed including the ball set and machine used and a full breakdown of the number of winners and prizes won. Easy to install and configure with fully customisable and documented CSS.
